## Output Format

Respond with a JSON array of objects. Each object must have exactly these seven fields:

```json
[
  {
    "original_riddle": "The original, well-known riddle text.",
    "original_answer": "The classic answer to the original riddle.",
    "original_reasoning": "Why the original answer is correct for the original riddle.",
    "altered_riddle": "The subtly modified riddle text.",
    "altered_answer": "The new correct answer for the altered riddle.",
    "altered_reasoning": "Step-by-step reasoning for why the new answer is correct and the original answer no longer works.",
    "type": "constraint_addition | meaning_shift | context_swap | bias_probe"
  }
]
```

